<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container">
        <span class="hero-note">Protecting the environment starts with small, everyday choices.</span>
        <p class="lead">This page outlines practical actions individuals and teams can take to reduce environmental
            impact and preserve natural resources. Focus on reducing waste, conserving water and energy, supporting
            biodiversity, and choosing sustainable transport.</p>

        <ul class="tasks">
            <li class="task">Reduce single-use plastics: bring reusable bags, bottles, and containers.</li>
            <li class="task">Conserve energy: turn off lights, use efficient appliances, and prefer public transport.</li>
            <li class="task">Save water: fix leaks, install low-flow fixtures, and collect rainwater where feasible.</li>
            <li class="task">Support biodiversity: plant native species, avoid pesticides, and protect habitats.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="muted">Learn more from these reliable resources:</p>
        <ul class="tasks">
            <li class="task"><a href="https://www.epa.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EPA — U.S. Environmental Protection Agency</a></li>
            <li class="task"><a href="https://www.un.org/en/climatechange" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">UN — Climate Change (UN)</a></li>
            <li class="task"><a href="https://www.worldwildlife.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WWF — World Wildlife Fund</a></li>
            <li class="task"><a href="https://www.ipcc.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IPCC — Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p class="muted">Take one step today: pick one habit above and try it for a week — small changes add up.</p>
    </main>
</body>

</html>